Name:           Djinn
Short Name:     djinn
Level Required: 8

Description:
  The Djinn is a humanoid creature from the Elemental Plane of Wind,
  using a Wind Sword and powerful bare-fisted punches to attack.

Commands:
  - summon djinn:   Summons it to you         (costs 30 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban djinn:      Banishes it               (costs 20 sp)
